high_descs: Go forward to the coffee machine.
Pick up the mug on the coffee machine.
Turn left and go to the sink.
Heat the mug in the microwave above the sink.
Take the heated mug in the microwave, turn around and head back to the coffee machine on the table.
Put the heated mug on the coffee machine.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated mug on the coffee machine.

high_descs: Face the coffee maker that is sitting on the white table in front of you
Pick up the coffee mug that is in the coffee machine in front of you
Turn left and head to the microwave that is above the sink across the room
Open the microwave and place the mug in the microwave the close the microwave and turn it on. Then open the microwave and pick up the mug and close the microwave door
Turn around and cross the room then turn to your left and face the coffee maker that is sitting on the white table
Place the mug in the coffee maker
anns.task_desc: Place a heated coffee mug in the coffee maker

high_descs: Look down at the counter directly in front.
Pick the cup up from the counter.
Go left and stand in front of the sink.
Put the cup in the microwave, shut the door and turn it on, open the door and take the cup out and shut the door.
Turn around and stand on the side of the table behind, on the side of the coffee maker.
Put the cup under the coffee pot on the table.
anns.task_desc: Put a cup under a coffee maker.

high_descs: Look at the table in front of you.
Grab the mug from inside the coffee machine.
Turn to your left and walk until you reach the microwave.
Warm the mug in the microwave, then take it out again.
Turn around and walk back to the table with the coffee machine on it.
Place the mug back inside the coffee machine.
anns.task_desc: Place a warmed mug in a coffee machine.
